#, no-c-format
msgid "Kernel Flavours"
msgstr "内核变种"

#. Tag: para
#: hardware.xml:1194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are four flavours of the powerpc kernel in Debian, based on the CPU "
"type:"
msgstr "在 Debian 中有四种基于 CPU 类型的 powerpc 内核："

